description: Trans World, TWA, Air France and other airlines come in for a landing but its Jake Corbin who arrives at San Francisco International airport that catches Jim Moore's eye.  Both guys contribute to the twink factor in the movie, lithe yet buff, sweet yet nasty, and both truly depict the eagerness of youth. Jake gives it to Jim so hard, the two boys travel across the length of the couch until Jim is propped against the armrest of the couch and has no choice but to take a merciless slamming from Jake.
title: Cruisin', Scene #04
